    {
      "title": "骑士94-115输活塞,哈登里程悲,一战看清5个现实:米神令人失望",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_3796a09191e76452",
      "snippet": "<p>北京时间5月16日,NBA季后赛迎来骑士与活塞系列赛的G6战｡在两队的天王山之战中,骑士一度落后15分,但是危难之际,哈登挺身而出,扶大厦之将倾,挽狂澜于既倒,全场拿到30分8篮板6助攻带队艰难取胜｡",
      "date": "2026-05-17 09:25:50"
    },
    {
      "title": "里奇-保罗:乔丹科比家庭完整所以自私,詹姆斯更愿帮助别人",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_0746a08a77941852",
      "snippet": "<p>里奇-保罗近日在播客节目《Million Dollaz Worth of Game》中再次力挺勒布朗-詹姆斯,并从成长环境角度解释了詹姆斯与迈克尔-乔丹､科比-布莱恩特在球场风格上的差异｡</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-3840235867-C205C6D49D9E766FC7B654717D7544B3/0?",
      "date": "2026-05-17 01:20:57"
    },
    {
      "title": "James Harden on MVP award, scoring title: 'I don't want to hear it' - ESPN",
      "link": "https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/12647566/james-harden-houston-rockets-focused-only-winning-not-awards",
      "snippet": "SAN ANTONIO -- James Harden didn't say a word when asked if he cares whether he wins the scoring title or the MVP award. The Rockets' James Harden says he is focused on winning, not MVP awards or scoring titles. AP Photo/Darron Cummings Harden, the Houston Rockets shooting guard who leads the league in scoring at 27.7 points and is one of the candidates for the MVP award, shook his head. When he finally spoke, Harden was pretty clear on what's important to him. \"I don't want to hear it, don't want to hear it,\" Harden said Thursday. \"The most important thing right now is winning. I've said it plenty of times; it's winning and getting a rhythm going into the postseason. We haven't had a great rhythm all year just because guys have been in and out of the lineup. For me, personally, I think for our team as well, is getting a rhythm and making sure everybody is on the same page. These five games will be important for us to catch our rhythm.\" The Rockets hold the No. 2 seed in the Western Co",
