    },
    {
      "title": "NBDL发展联盟",
      "link": "https://baike.sogou.com/v7728716.htm",
      "snippet": "\"NBDL含义 NBDL是NBA发展联盟(NBA Development League)的缩写,属于NBA的二级联盟,是NBA的人才库,此联盟多为参加过NBA选秀或季前赛的球员｡ NBA的任何球队都可以在发展联盟里选球员进入NBA,也可以将自己队中的球员下放到发展联盟里锻炼｡ 一般来说,NBDL与所属NBA球队在战术打法,甚至防守策略上都一样.因为NBDL就是为了个母队储备所需人才的.",
      "date": "2024-12-19 22:06:29"
    },
    {
      "title": "2025 NBA Playoffs Calendar: Key Dates and the Play-In Tournament Explained_teams_for_April",
      "link": "https://www.sohu.com/a/880078943_122342248",
      "snippet": "As the conclusion of the NBA season approaches, anticipation for the playoffs builds. Fans, teams, and analysts alike are closely monitoring the standings as each game can dramatically sway a team's fate. In this article, we will explore the critical dates for the upcoming 2025 NBA playoffs, the significance of the play-in tournament, and the current playoff picture. Understanding the Play-In Tournament Scheduled from April 15 to April 18, the play-in tournament is a fascinating aspect of the NBA postseason format. This mini-tournament involves teams ranked seventh through tenth in both the Eastern and Western Conferences. During these high-stakes games, every possession matters. For instance, the seventh-seed team will face the eighth-seed, with the winner earning a spot in the playoffs. Simultaneously, the ninth-seed will compete against the tenth-seed, where the victor moves on to face the loser of the first matchup for the final playoff berth. This thrilling format not only keeps t",
      "date": "2025-04-05 14:08:00"
    },
    {
      "title": "威尔·康罗",
      "link": "https://baike.baidu.com/item/威尔·康罗/10322340",
      "snippet": "\"威尔·康罗是美国NBDL(NBA Development League)球员｡个人简介技术特点有点像罗伊和内特-罗宾逊,是一个具备极高水准的球员,同时他是一个典型的速度型后卫,具备极强的突破能力｡ 康罗在NBDL表现十分抢眼,因此06-07赛季他有机会在NBA快船和灰熊队效力,不过绝对属于末流球员,一个赛季总共只打了7场比赛,登场14分钟没有得分只得到7个篮板和9次助攻｡",
      "date": "2026-05-17 09:28:13"
    },
    {
      "title": "2026 NBA Playoffs  Official Site",
      "link": "http://www.nbafinals.com/",
      "snippet": "LATEST PLAYOFF NEWS Recap: Knicks go up 2-0, Spurs pull even Check out the best from Wednesday's action in the 2026 NBA Conference Semifinals with our live blog. Overwhelming start fuels Spurs in Game 2 San Antonio shows intensity and resiliency from the opening tip to overwhelm Minnesota with a 133-95 home victory. Knicks survive tense 4th to take 2-0 lead In a game featuring 25 lead changes, New York leans on a late 9-0 run to turn back Philadelphia 108-102 in Game 2. Knicks 4th quarter run propels them to 2-0 series lead The New York Knicks go on a 9-0 4th quarter run to propel them to a 2-0 series lead over the Sixers. Cavs look to match Pistons' energy in Game 2 Cleveland will look to clean things up on both sides of the ball, while Detroit tries to open a 2-0 series lead. Lakers need Reaves to deliver in Game 2 The Lakers understand their playoff dilemma. They need to be near their best to win, and the defending champ Thunder do not.  OKC's bigs stand tall in Game 1 win vs. Laker",
